even more frightening than Jong Sook?]

106
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:40,770
[Park Bo Young]

107
00:06:42,330 --> 00:06:44,670
[The embodiment of ferociousness, Bo Young.]

108
00:06:44,670 --> 00:06:51,490
