you've already kissed Jae Suk?

135
00:08:24,890 --> 00:08:27,980
[Man killer, Kwang Ja?]

136
00:08:27,990 --> 00:08:30,650
- I can't believe that Jong Suk is here.
- Really... Jong Suk.

137
00:08:30,650 --> 00:08:35,120
[The boys team's image has skyrocketed
with Jong Suk joining their team.]

138
00:08:35,130 --> 00:08:37,700
These three girls are all starry-eyed.

139
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:40,740
