they've all fallen for him already.

140
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:43,530
- You look like you've fallen for him too.
- No, not me.

141
00:08:43,530 --> 00:08:45,840
[Even Jong Sook is
getting a little starry-eyed?]

142
00:08:46,340 --> 00:08:48,410
