143
00:08:48,410 --> 00:08:51,390
- Just keep adding Yoo Jae Suk.
- No!

144
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:53,790
- I know that you still have feelings for her.
- Me?

145
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:56,150
[Jae Suk still has feelings for Kwang Ja?]

146
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:58,490
