between the male and female students.

149
00:09:10,730 --> 00:09:16,990
You will be competing male vs female students
to end the battle for once and for all.

150
00:09:16,990 --> 00:09:19,450
The race that you all will be
participating in today...

151
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:23,250
is called, the Rural Romance.

152
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:26,280
- Rural?
- Are we going out to a farm?

153
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:29,160
- We're not...
- You're not...

154
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:31,820
- Not the rice paddy, is it?
- In the middle of this cold winter?

155
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:34,110
Who would be crazy enough to go out
to a rice paddy in this kind of weather?

156
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:37,580
- Our producers would.
- No way.

157
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:39,260
[You know us well.]

158
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:47,290
[But... there's a couple who's been dating
in secret amongst this group.]

159
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,610
- We made each other a promise.
- Who is it?

160
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:59,430
[Attacks Jong Suk?]

161
00:10:01,850 --> 00:10:03,490
He just sniffed me.

162
00:10:04,430 --> 00:10:06,470
I didn't sniff you!

163
00:10:06,470 --> 00:10:11,150
- When did I sniff you?
- This race is to find out who the couple is.

164
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:14,240
[Find out who the secret lovebirds are!]

165
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:17,870
[A hint to help them find out who the secret
couple is will be given to the game winners.]

166
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:23,480
[Will it be the secret couple's victory,
or the rest of the students' victory?]

167
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,840
