168
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:27,260
So you must find out who the tragic,
and desperate couple is.

169
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:32,080
[Which of the two are involved
in a secret love affair?]

170
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,420
<i>It's not me, so you're all dead.

171
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:39,260
[But why... is Jong Suk acting like that?]

