Jong Suk received?]

175
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,760
<i>Hi Jong Suk.

176
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:57,930
<i>I feel like this secret love affair
that we've been having...

177
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:04,570
<i>I feel like it's been quite a while already
since we've started this secret love affair.

178
00:11:04,570 --> 00:11:06,560
[Jong Suk is one of the star crossed lovers.]

179
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:10,660
<i>I know that everyone in this school is
constantly at each other's throats.

180
00:11:10,660 --> 00:11:16,920
<i>So I'm sure that they'll all go crazy if they
find out that we're dating in secret, right?

181
00:11:20,140 --> 00:11:24,250
