between the boys and the girls today.

182
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:29,270
<i>But if we succeed the mission without
others finding out that we're a couple

183
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:32,300
<i>then I'm told that we no longer
have to keep dating in secret.

184
00:11:34,210 --> 00:11:35,540
Who could it be?

185
00:11:36,230 --> 00:11:38,040
Who is...

186
00:11:38,690 --> 00:11:40,390
What do I do?

187
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:45,640
To be involved in a secret love affair
in this day and age...

188
00:11:48,090 --> 00:11:51,610
