but you won't tell me who it is?

189
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:56,500
[Sweet and innocent Jong Suk is nervous
just at the mention of a secret affair.]

190
00:11:57,530 --> 00:12:00,400
Who would you like for your
girlfriend to be?

191
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:04,340
A girl who has a pretty neck...

192
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,370
with a bit of an obsessive personality.

193
00:12:09,850 --> 00:12:11,800
I want to be loved.

194
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:22,310
[Who could be his girlfriend
who sent him this letter?]

195
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:33,890
[She's here!]

196
00:12:36,530 --> 00:12:40,560
[Jong Suk's secret girlfriend
is none other than...]

197
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:43,690
Is he my partner?
Thank you!

198
00:12:45,230 --> 00:12:48,820
[Running High's Juliet, Ji Hyo.]

199
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:51,230
- I'm his girlfriend?
- He's your boyfriend.

200
00:12:52,730 --> 00:12:55,750
What took you so long to come clean
about our relationship?

201
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:59,140
- I didn't even know that we were dating.
- I know. Me neither.

202
00:12:59,140 --> 00:13:03,760
[Running High's Romeo and Juliet-
Jong Suk and Ji Hyo.]

203
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:07,110
- What should we do?
- I don't really understand it.

204
00:13:07,110 --> 00:13:11,580
You don't understand?
My partner's intelligence level is a bit...

205
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:16,220
No, that was just a joke.

206
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:18,030
We need to be confirmed as a couple.

207
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:23,490
[Girlfriend Blank Ji is calmly explaining
today's race to him.]

208
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:27,990
This mission is saying that we have to imitate
the pose that two of the producers

209
00:13:27,990 --> 00:13:30,970
are doing for three seconds.

210
00:13:30,980 --> 00:13:36,560
We need to do it when we're around the other
members and make it pretty obvious

211
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:39,000
but we have to make sure not to
get caught by them.

212
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:41,600
- Do you understand it now?
- So make sure not to get caught, right?

213
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:45,630
- Without anyone knowing.
- Hold the pose for three seconds.

214
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:49,330
[Their couple mission is going to get
increasingly more difficult with each game.]

215
00:13:49,330 --> 00:13:54,690
[If they succeed their own missions,
they can give out fake hints to others.]

216
00:13:54,690 --> 00:13:58,480
[More fake hints that are given out,
then more advantageous it'll be for them.]

217
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:01,470
- Let's do our best today, boyfriend.
- Yes, Ma'am... I mean, okay.

218
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:06,350
You're not doing this for your love,
but this is to win the gold...

219
00:14:06,350 --> 00:14:08,570
No, we're in love.

220
00:14:08,570 --> 00:14:10,200
Yes, we're in love.

221
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,610
We're in love, but this is only
our second time seeing each other.

222
00:14:12,610 --> 00:14:14,260
- So we're just feeling a little shy.
- We're just a little shy right now.

223
00:14:14,260 --> 00:14:17,500
We really are boyfriend and girlfriend,
but we're feeling a little shy right now.

224
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:20,550
- Just let us be in love.
- Just leave our love be.

225
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:23,570
Just allow us to be in love.
Why do we have to keep our love a secret?

226
00:14:23,570 --> 00:14:26,810
This is only the second time that we're
seeing each other in a whole year.

227
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:31,840
[Anyways, Jong Suk and Ji Hyo
are the secret couple.]

228
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:35,900
