There they come.
They're scary.

460
00:30:48,690 --> 00:30:51,120
[Full of desire to win.]

461
00:30:56,330 --> 00:30:58,290
[Knocked off with one shove.]

462
00:31:05,340 --> 00:31:08,120
[Blank Ji and Bo Young takes that opportunity
to pull themselves up onto the platform.]

463
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:16,920
[Where are they taking him?]

464
00:31:16,920 --> 00:31:18,520
- What are you guys doing?
- That's enough!

465
00:31:26,330 --> 00:31:29,950
[Big-nose ultimately is brought back
to his starting line.]

466
00:31:29,950 --> 00:31:31,880
Why haven't you started yet?

467
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:36,170
You're the only one left to pass.

468
00:31:43,520 --> 00:31:45,540
[Time over]

469
00:31:45,540 --> 00:31:49,140
[Blank Ji and Bo Young
easily pass the round.]

470
00:31:49,140 --> 00:31:51,820
- You have to conserve your energy.
- We're still in the lead.

471
00:31:53,010 --> 00:31:55,480
[Anyway, Blank Ji
thankfully passes the round.]

472
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:59,650
[The two are finally brought closer...]

473
00:31:59,650 --> 00:32:02,030
[The arm link mission.]

474
00:32:02,030 --> 00:32:09,650
[This is their last chance.]

475
00:32:11,130 --> 00:32:14,250
- Let's just give up.
- No, you can't give up.

476
00:32:14,250 --> 00:32:17,790
[But Bo Young and Sae Young are
standing between the two.]

477
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:21,050
[Blank Ji casually turns around to
move closer to Jong Suk.]

478
00:32:26,570 --> 00:32:33,060
[While everyone’s attention is focused
on the last bit of the game...]

479
00:32:34,160 --> 00:32:37,460
[Oh?]

480
00:32:37,460 --> 00:32:45,120
[Jong Suk pulls Ji Hyo to him.]

481
00:32:49,540 --> 00:32:54,510
[Jong Suk and Ji Hyo succeeds in their
mission to link their arms together.]

482
00:32:57,450 --> 00:32:59,400
[Oh?]

483
00:32:59,410 --> 00:33:02,970
[Bo Young's gaze...]

484
00:33:03,660 --> 00:33:06,300
[And Gary too?]

485
00:33:06,300 --> 00:33:10,470
[Did they see?]

486
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:12,000
Try and come this time.

487
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:17,800
[Whew... they fortunately didn't
seem to notice.]

488
00:33:24,470 --> 00:33:28,660
[While everyone's focused on
what's going on in the game...]

489
00:33:28,660 --> 00:33:34,180
[This time, Ji Hyo links her arm
through Jong Suk's!]

490
00:33:34,180 --> 00:33:39,190
[Heart is beating fast...]

491
00:33:45,930 --> 00:33:53,230
[Their hidden secret...
amongst these people...]

492
00:33:53,230 --> 00:33:58,650
[Jong Suk and Ji Hyo succeed
their first mission.]

493
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:04,960
[Then shall we observe Big-nose's
humiliation in peace now?]

494
00:34:10,090 --> 00:34:12,550
[Big-nose shoves Jong Sook off the platform!]

495
00:34:13,580 --> 00:34:16,460
[It's still anyone's game!]

496
00:34:22,900 --> 00:34:26,250
[Big-nose could miraculously
win this game?]

497
00:34:30,830 --> 00:34:33,480
[Big-nose is showing off his fighting spirit.]

498
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:35,820
You have to get up there!

499
00:34:52,060 --> 00:34:54,610
Pull your feet up off the ground.
That'll count as you being up there.

500
00:34:58,110 --> 00:35:00,110
[Straw platform- Game over.]

501
00:35:00,110 --> 00:35:02,090
Why did you lift one foot
off the ground?

502
00:35:03,340 --> 00:35:06,440
Did you and Jong Sook kiss or something?
Why did you lift one foot off the ground?

503
00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:10,300
We won!

504
00:35:10,300 --> 00:35:12,040
[Rural Romance Race-
Girls Team wins the first mission.]

505
00:35:12,050 --> 00:35:13,840
They're really good at planning.

506
00:35:14,940 --> 00:35:20,490
And thus, the girl team took the win
in our first physical mission.

507
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:23,860
[Total and utter humiliation.]

508
00:35:24,430 --> 00:35:26,860
Maybe the guys were just trying to be
gentlemen, and went easy on us?

509
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:29,680
We wouldn't have been able to win
otherwise.

510
00:35:30,650 --> 00:35:32,570
You two, seriously...

511
00:35:32,570 --> 00:35:35,990
If you weren't a girl...
Let's go, just you and me.

512
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:40,310
[One on one?]

513
00:35:40,310 --> 00:35:42,010
- Lee Jong Suk and...
- What did you say?

514
00:35:42,010 --> 00:35:44,080
And Kim Jong Sook.
A one on one match between those two.

515
00:35:44,080 --> 00:35:46,100
We're not going to go easy on you.

516
00:35:46,100 --> 00:35:49,370
- An unexpected win...
- What do you mean, unexpected?

517
00:35:50,430 --> 00:35:52,210
You really are being too much.

518
00:35:52,210 --> 00:35:54,310
You guys are such gentlemen.

519
00:35:56,370 --> 00:35:57,870
You guys are gentlemen.

520
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:14,970
You should've been more gentle with him!

521
00:36:14,970 --> 00:36:16,580
[Samson Jong Sook.]

522
00:36:16,580 --> 00:36:18,620
Gentlemen!

523
00:36:20,070 --> 00:36:22,470
- They're such gentlemen.
- Thank you.

524
00:36:22,470 --> 00:36:24,620
- Thank you.
- We really are gentlemen though.

525
00:36:24,620 --> 00:36:27,460
- Of course, we are.
- The Girls' Team wins.

526
00:36:28,330 --> 00:36:32,230
[The Girls' Team wins a hint about the
secret couple from having won the mission.]

527
00:36:32,230 --> 00:36:38,830
[One fake and one real hint from Jong Suk
and Ji Hyo having succeeded their mission.]

528
00:36:38,830 --> 00:36:42,130
[Even though it's a relief,
she still can't help but feel nervous...]

529
00:36:42,130 --> 00:36:43,460
I'm so angry right now.

530
00:36:43,460 --> 00:36:47,940
The men are looking so exhausted that I think
we need to stop for our meal before moving on.

531
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:49,580
Let's play another game before we eat!

532
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:53,640
- Let's show them what us girls are made of!
- Working out on an empty stomach is best!

533
00:36:59,990 --> 00:37:01,840
I'm done.
I'm done with that.

534
00:37:09,240 --> 00:37:14,530
[Real hint and a fake hint.]

535
00:37:15,810 --> 00:37:18,810
<i>Rural Romance Race.
Go to the greenhouse in Namchon.

536
00:37:18,810 --> 00:37:20,690
[Next location- The greenhouse.]

537
00:37:20,690 --> 00:37:24,370
- What were the hints that we received?
- Let's look at the hints.

538
00:37:24,380 --> 00:37:27,680
Were you two not going to show us
the hints if we hadn't said anything?

539
00:37:27,680 --> 00:37:29,940
- You two are acting funny.
- No, it's not like that.

540
00:37:30,390 --> 00:37:31,860
There are two hints.

541
00:37:31,870 --> 00:37:34,940
- Mine said, 'P and K'.
- Mine says 'J'.

542
00:37:34,940 --> 00:37:36,780
- P and K?
- Yes.

543
00:37:36,780 --> 00:37:39,310
- Let me see.
- What could that be for?

544
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:42,680
- PK and JK?
- No, PK and J.

545
00:37:42,680 --> 00:37:47,500
- 'J' could mean Jae Suk, Jong Kook...
- Who's PK?

546
00:37:47,500 --> 00:37:50,120
- 'P' would only be Bo Young.
- Who's PK?

547
00:37:50,120 --> 00:37:53,910
[Confusing to figure out
which one of the two is the real hint.]

548
00:37:54,140 --> 00:37:57,100
If that hint is indicating towards me,
then that's the fake hint.

549
00:37:58,050 --> 00:38:00,310
- We'll be the judge of that.
- She makes it sound simple.

550
00:38:03,240 --> 00:38:07,300
[Just then, they receive a call
from Ha Ha.]

551
00:38:08,540 --> 00:38:11,440
- We've figured out who the guy is.
- Just unbelievable.

552
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:14,660
<i>- We've figured out who the guy is.
- Just unbelievable.

553
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:19,950
[Did Jong Suk get found out?]

554
00:38:19,950 --> 00:38:21,930
It's Yoo Jae Suk.

555
00:38:21,930 --> 00:38:23,880
It's Yoo Jae Suk.

556
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:29,750
[The guys still believe that
Jae Suk is the culprit.]

557
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:31,310
<i>It's Yoo Jae Suk?

558
00:38:32,420 --> 00:38:34,220
- Yoo Jae Suk is the guy, okay?
- Okay.

559
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:37,280
Take a look at all the girls' faces,
and see who looks most flustered.

560
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:41,540
I didn't know you were Jae Suk's style.

561
00:38:44,110 --> 00:38:46,450
- Find out who the culprit is on your end.
- Okay, we got it.

562
00:38:46,450 --> 00:38:48,510
[If they think it's Jae Suk...
then that's a huge relief.]

563
00:38:48,540 --> 00:38:51,700
[I'm doing really good at this.]

564
00:38:51,700 --> 00:38:53,410
Pink is my favorite color.

565
00:38:56,100 --> 00:38:57,380
What is this?

566
00:38:57,380 --> 00:39:01,160
[Which couple awaits for
Jong Suk and Ji Hyo this time?]

567
00:39:05,660 --> 00:39:07,990
[Jong Suk and Ji Hyo's second mission-
Clasped hands.]

568
00:39:10,300 --> 00:39:12,410
[Oh my God...]

569
00:39:13,730 --> 00:39:16,590
[One step above the linked arm mission!]

570
00:39:17,490 --> 00:39:21,860
[To have to clasp our hands together
without others seeing...]

571
00:39:21,860 --> 00:39:23,580
Why am I supposed to do that?

572
00:39:28,070 --> 00:39:30,060
- This must be the place.
- Lets go inside.

573
00:39:30,060 --> 00:39:31,880
- Let's just go inside.
- No reason to even hesitate about this.

574
00:39:32,290 --> 00:39:35,310
[The boys team arrives soon thereafter.]

575
00:39:43,610 --> 00:39:46,320
[Oh my... that's much harder...]

576
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:48,340
- Are you leaving your phone behind?
- What's with those two?

577
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:53,820
- What are you two doing?
- We're just saying 'hi'.

578
00:39:53,820 --> 00:39:55,760
What are you guys doing?

579
00:39:56,310 --> 00:39:57,820
Congratulations.

580
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,590
Are you two having a little lovers' chat?

581
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:05,890
[Gary seriously thinks that
these two are dating...]

582
00:40:07,050 --> 00:40:11,680
[But this is a difficult mission.
Will they be able to succeed?]

583
00:40:11,680 --> 00:40:15,570
- Hurry it up!
- What took you so long?

584
00:40:15,570 --> 00:40:19,810
[These girls are quite prickly from their...
hormonal teenage years?]

585
00:40:19,810 --> 00:40:22,350
- You're not gentlemen after all.
- You guys are unbelievable.

586
00:40:22,350 --> 00:40:23,630
Look here.

587
00:40:23,630 --> 00:40:25,260
You little princesses.

588
00:40:25,950 --> 00:40:29,710
Stop just calling us princesses,
and start treating us like princesses.

589
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:32,930
You guys should've gotten here faster.

590
00:40:32,940 --> 00:40:35,120
[Bickering already before
the game has even begun.]

591
00:40:35,120 --> 00:40:37,160
Kang Gary, you've gotten so ugly.

592
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:40,870
[Why are you saying such a thing
out of the blue?]

593
00:40:40,870 --> 00:40:44,460
Your next game has to do with
the horizontal bar that you see there.

594
00:40:44,460 --> 00:40:46,560
That's why we've named this game,
The Scarecrow.

595
00:40:46,560 --> 00:40:48,060
- What is that?
- The Scarecrow?

596
00:40:48,060 --> 00:40:50,290
- Isn't she it?
- Do we have to hang from it?

597
00:40:50,290 --> 00:40:52,140
[Scarecrow doppelganger, Kwang Soo-crow.]

598
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:56,120
[It's a game that brings back
memories from their own childhood.]

599
00:40:56,660 --> 00:40:58,790
[What kind of a game is that?]

600
00:40:59,950 --> 00:41:03,790
['70-'80 men who step up to
personally demonstrate the game.]

601
00:41:03,790 --> 00:41:09,950
[Win the game by avoiding the other team,
and making your way back within four moves.]

602
00:41:09,950 --> 00:41:13,040
- You have to put your arms around my leg.
- Scarecrow.

603
00:41:18,220 --> 00:41:21,380
[Lovers quarrel with his ex-girlfriend,
Kwang Ja, that never seems to cease.]

604
00:41:21,390 --> 00:41:24,090
It's your own fault for confessing your love
to me when you knew I didn't love you.

605
00:41:24,090 --> 00:41:27,190
- Did you really confess your love for her?
- I'm seriously going to lose my mind.

606
00:41:27,190 --> 00:41:30,240
[Short relationship,
and a lifetime of regrets.]

607
00:41:30,240 --> 00:41:33,130
- We're going to play a round as a test.
- Okay, let's go.

608
00:41:33,710 --> 00:41:36,780
[Big-nose and Sae Young to play
Rock-Paper-Scissors to see who'll go first.]

609
00:41:36,780 --> 00:41:37,950
[Big-nose wins.]

610
00:41:37,950 --> 00:41:39,760
You're supposed to throw a 'Rock'
if you're a man.

611
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:41,540
So why did you throw a rock?

612
00:41:41,540 --> 00:41:44,370
- Yeah, why did you do that?
- Are you two dating?

613
00:41:44,370 --> 00:41:46,000
You know that's not possible.

614
00:41:50,790 --> 00:41:53,260
You have to play defense.
You can block him.

615
00:41:54,950 --> 00:41:59,440
- Scarecrow!
- Okay!

616
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:01,820
[Hyuk completely blocks off a path.]

617
00:42:04,320 --> 00:42:07,170
- I see your underpants!
- Stop it!

618
00:42:10,640 --> 00:42:13,970
- Scare...
- You have to help us out too.

619
00:42:14,250 --> 00:42:16,390
[Why is she dangling from the bar?]

620
00:42:21,620 --> 00:42:24,350
[What is this?]

621
00:42:25,980 --> 00:42:27,460
Okay, fine.
We'll let you do that.

622
00:42:27,460 --> 00:42:29,860
You still have to make
three more moves, Kwang Soo.

623
00:42:29,860 --> 00:42:31,950
- What?
- You only made one of the four moves.

624
00:42:31,950 --> 00:42:33,800
I have to do all that?

625
00:42:33,800 --> 00:42:37,810
[Only made one move out of the four...]

626
00:42:42,190 --> 00:42:45,150
If you oust yourself, I'm going to...

627
00:42:45,720 --> 00:42:48,000
[His second move.]

628
00:42:48,010 --> 00:42:49,670
Do you think that you're
an acrobat or something?

629
00:42:49,680 --> 00:42:54,290
- I'm going to get you for that.
- You've still got two moves left to make.

630
00:42:54,290 --> 00:42:56,510
Two more moves.

631
00:42:58,160 --> 00:43:02,050
[He now has to remain in this position
without budging to the end.]

632
00:43:02,500 --> 00:43:04,340
He has to stay in that position?

633
00:43:06,050 --> 00:43:07,610
Please hurry!

634
00:43:12,430 --> 00:43:13,790
Please!

635
00:43:13,790 --> 00:43:16,710
[Ha Ha finishes surrounding Kwang Soo.]

636
00:43:22,670 --> 00:43:24,840
[Same plan as Jae Suk.
Bo Young blocks the other side.]

637
00:43:24,840 --> 00:43:26,950
I think this one will be ousted soon.

638
00:43:30,720 --> 00:43:32,950
[Big-nose brother's turn.]

639
00:43:40,610 --> 00:43:46,230
[Easy Brothers' Parallel Theory.]

640
00:43:48,670 --> 00:43:50,490
Why don't we just leave him
to stay in that position?

641
00:43:50,490 --> 00:43:51,950
[Easy Brothers are no threat to anyone
by being stuck in their current position.]

642
00:43:51,950 --> 00:43:54,180
Are you two playing a game,
or being punished right now?

643
00:43:54,540 --> 00:43:56,480
Okay, I'll go this time.

644
00:43:56,480 --> 00:43:59,160
[Just then, Blank Ji makes her move.]

645
00:44:00,150 --> 00:44:02,460
I think his feet are too far up.

646
00:44:02,470 --> 00:44:06,060
[Should we slowly...
start to make our move?]

647
00:44:06,060 --> 00:44:11,520
[Secret couple's second mission-
Clasp their hands together.]

648
00:44:11,520 --> 00:44:13,980
[What is Blank Ji's plan?]

649
00:44:18,280 --> 00:44:21,070
[That's our ace!
Getting as far away as she could from others.]

650
00:44:21,070 --> 00:44:22,740
[Come close to me, Jong Suk.]

651
00:44:22,740 --> 00:44:25,110
[I'll be there soon.
Wait for me!]

652
00:44:26,040 --> 00:44:30,810
[Just then...
Gary makes his move over to Ji Hyo!]

653
00:44:33,430 --> 00:44:36,020
[It's too dangerous to get close
to Ji Hyo at this rate!]

654
00:44:37,070 --> 00:44:39,610
- I don't know what to do about this.
- Hurry up!

655
00:44:39,610 --> 00:44:41,800
He's stepping on the line.

656
00:44:41,800 --> 00:44:43,820
Hurry up, Jong Suk!

657
00:44:48,630 --> 00:44:51,310
[Makes his move towards Ji Hyo
without any hesitation.]

658
00:44:52,650 --> 00:44:54,880
Why are we always involved
in a love triangle?

659
00:44:54,880 --> 00:44:56,370
[What do I do now?]

660
00:45:01,950 --> 00:45:07,810
[Now they have to get back to the starting
line without touching their opponents.]

661
00:45:10,440 --> 00:45:13,090
[Yoo Hyuk succeeds.]

662
00:45:25,260 --> 00:45:27,440
[Kwang Ja is eliminated.]

663
00:45:28,130 --> 00:45:30,120
[Exhaustion hits...]

664
00:45:31,040 --> 00:45:32,630
[Haroro also succeeds with ease.]

665
00:45:32,630 --> 00:45:34,970
- One to...
- It's two to zero.

666
00:45:34,970 --> 00:45:39,670
[Secret couple could've done their mission
by now if it hadn't been for Gary...]

667
00:45:43,670 --> 00:45:47,080
[While everyone's eyes and ears
are focused towards the bar...]

668
00:45:47,080 --> 00:45:50,110
[But they're afraid of getting caught
with their hand clasped in each other's...]

669
00:45:59,160 --> 00:46:02,280
[The game is slowly coming to an end...]

670
00:46:05,210 --> 00:46:08,170
[But to do their mission...]

671
00:46:08,170 --> 00:46:12,850
[There's just not enough time!]

672
00:46:14,610 --> 00:46:17,360
[And it's all because of this one man.]

673
00:46:17,970 --> 00:46:19,430
Okay, My turn.

674
00:46:25,730 --> 00:46:28,480
[Ji Hyo purposely jumped far out to do
her secret mission, but her plan backfired.]

675
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:33,530
[Having lost her chance at the secret mission,
Ji Hyo still succeeds in this public mission.]

676
00:46:34,240 --> 00:46:38,440
[Ah... we were so close.]

677
00:46:39,630 --> 00:46:41,220
We'll go first.

678
00:46:43,140 --> 00:46:46,330
[First round was a tie.
This round to determine the winner.]

679
00:46:47,080 --> 00:46:48,740
- Should I go first?
- Okay.

680
00:46:50,550 --> 00:46:52,350
You stepped on the line.

681
00:46:54,840 --> 00:46:57,410
[Blocking the immediate area
like they had done before.]

682
00:46:57,410 --> 00:47:00,570
[But it's not easy to maintain
a position like that...]

683
00:47:00,570 --> 00:47:03,990
- I bet Sae Young will do it.
- I'm going to go out this way.

684
00:47:03,990 --> 00:47:10,590
[Ha Ha makes his move to block Sae Young.]

685
00:47:15,590 --> 00:47:17,580
- We can block that area too.
- Yeah, let's block it.

686
00:47:17,580 --> 00:47:19,850
- You want me to stay close?
- Yes, don't go too far out.

687
00:47:20,870 --> 00:47:24,500
[Bo Young goes to keep the other end
blocked off for the opposing team.]

688
00:47:27,800 --> 00:47:30,030
- There you go.
- I can still do it.

689
00:47:31,310 --> 00:47:35,190
[Sae Young is surrounded by Ha Ha and
Gary on either side of her.]

690
00:47:36,020 --> 00:47:37,610
- Okay, next.
- Who's going next?

691
00:47:37,610 --> 00:47:40,080
Should I go next?

692
00:47:40,080 --> 00:47:43,260
