01:02:25,700 --> 01:02:27,290
You don't know what this is...

923
01:02:27,290 --> 01:02:31,880
But you have to complete whichever mission
you are given within three minutes

924
01:02:31,880 --> 01:02:33,990
which includes your shopping time.

925
01:02:35,830 --> 01:02:40,340
[Off to the market for now
to buy the stuff that they need.]

926
01:02:40,340 --> 01:02:43,060
[They must return within three minutes!]

927
01:02:52,720 --> 01:02:55,030
[A market with countless number
of goodies to buy...]

928
01:02:55,030 --> 01:02:58,290
[What will they bring back?]

929
01:02:58,290 --> 01:03:00,700
- What about the dried persimmon?
- That's what we wanted to get.

930
01:03:00,700 --> 01:03:03,730
[Unsure of what to buy since they
don't know what the mission is.]

931
01:03:03,730 --> 01:03:05,900
- You want to buy clementines?
- Yes, I think clementines would be best.

932
01:03:05,900 --> 01:03:08,000
You're thinking clementines?
Okay, let's buy clementines.

933
01:03:08,000 --> 01:03:09,480
[Suk Jin and Sae Young buy clementines.]

934
01:03:09,490 --> 01:03:11,100
Something like this?

935
01:03:11,100 --> 01:03:13,310
How about some rice?
Want to buy rice?

936
01:03:14,360 --> 01:03:16,000
- How about tofu?
- Okay, tofu.

937
01:03:16,000 --> 01:03:18,580
Can you give us a piece of the tofu?

938
01:03:19,220 --> 01:03:21,570
[Kwang Soo and Gary buy a piece of tofu.]

939
01:03:24,230 --> 01:03:28,120
[Another team has already
bought the clementines...]

940
01:03:28,120 --> 01:03:29,780
How about this?
Dried persimmons.

941
01:03:29,780 --> 01:03:31,940
[Jong Kook and Ha Ha buy dried persimmons.]

942
01:03:31,940 --> 01:03:34,410
- Here's 5,000 won.
- Thank you.

943
01:03:35,080 --> 01:03:38,040
- Want to buy the mackerel?
- Did you see the mission?

944
01:03:38,080 --> 01:03:40,510
- Did you see the mission?
- Yeah, the forehead kiss.

945
01:03:41,880 --> 01:03:44,600
[Third secret couple mission-
Forehead kiss.]

946
01:03:45,090 --> 01:03:47,520
- It's a forehead to forehead to kiss.
- We have to touch our foreheads together?

947
01:03:47,520 --> 01:03:50,160
Let's buy something first.
How about jujubes?

948
01:03:50,160 --> 01:03:53,540
- How about the anchovies?
- How much are the jujubes?

949
01:03:53,540 --> 01:03:55,850
[Trying to buy what they need
to do their mission first...]

950
01:03:55,850 --> 01:03:58,450
- How much is this?
- 5,000 won.

951
01:03:59,090 --> 01:04:00,380
What is that?

952
01:04:00,380 --> 01:04:03,100
[Ji Hyo sees Jae Suk and Bo Young
passing them by.]

953
01:04:03,660 --> 01:04:06,100
Just buy whatever.
Let's touch our foreheads together now.

954
01:04:06,100 --> 01:04:08,890
[What?
They're going to do it right here?]

955
01:04:10,480 --> 01:04:14,260
[With no one else around...
with the added thrill and excitement.]

956
01:04:17,390 --> 01:04:21,380
[Almost there!]

957
01:04:23,540 --> 01:04:26,050
[Jae Suk couple suddenly turns and
heads back towards Jong Suk and Ji Hyo.]

958
01:04:29,310 --> 01:04:32,550
[Rushing to buy their merchandise
when they hear someone coming close by.]

959
01:04:38,800 --> 01:04:40,610
Hey, let's go get the clementines!

960
01:04:40,610 --> 01:04:45,570
[The forehead kiss...
Did they just fail their first attempt?]

961
01:04:46,740 --> 01:04:49,620
[Ji Hyo and Jong Suk are first to get back.]

962
01:04:49,620 --> 01:04:51,490
Right here.

963
01:04:51,490 --> 01:04:54,560
[Kwang Ja and Gary arrive soon thereafter.]

964
01:04:59,060 --> 01:05:01,430
Don't let go of each other's hands.
Two minutes have passed.

965
01:05:01,430 --> 01:05:04,180
- Everyone back?
- Yes, we're all here.

966
01:05:04,190 --> 01:05:06,200
[Everyone is back on set.]

967
01:05:06,200 --> 01:05:07,660
Look at the mission that you've chosen.

968
01:05:07,660 --> 01:05:10,220
[The mission they need to do
with the purchase they made is...]

969
01:05:12,280 --> 01:05:15,640
[Pile the items that you bought
in a tower within a minute.]

970
01:05:17,430 --> 01:05:20,190
- We all bought the same thing?
- Let's use the tofu first.

971
01:05:20,190 --> 01:05:22,760
Why did you buy clementines?

972
01:05:22,760 --> 01:05:26,090
- Look at how nice this tofu is.
- Can we stack it like this?

973
01:05:26,090 --> 01:05:29,060
- How do you want us to stack these?
- Just stack them.

974
01:05:29,060 --> 01:05:32,580
[They have to stack all the odds and ends
that they bought and brought back?]

975
01:05:35,980 --> 01:05:37,970
- Stack them up together.
- Just start stacking them.

976
01:05:40,170 --> 01:05:42,190
- Stack them like this.
- I have dried persimmons.

977
01:05:42,200 --> 01:05:44,810
[The time is ticking, and
there are so many things to stack!]

978
01:05:45,670 --> 01:05:47,760
- Put it on the bottom.
- More clementines.

979
01:05:47,760 --> 01:05:49,790
You've got ten seconds left.

980
01:05:49,790 --> 01:05:53,890
- Okay, I think we got it.
- Oh no!

981
01:05:56,630 --> 01:05:58,480
[Time over]

982
01:06:03,510 --> 01:06:06,610
[Unfortunately fails the mission
because of one little clementine.]

983
01:06:06,610 --> 01:06:09,880
- We never should've ripped the bag.
- Who opened up the bag of clementines?

984
01:06:09,880 --> 01:06:13,010
- Why did you rip the bag open?
- No, it's okay.

985
01:06:13,010 --> 01:06:16,130
It's really good though.

986
01:06:16,130 --> 01:06:19,020
[Time for a little snack break.]

987
01:06:19,020 --> 01:06:21,680
But this was a much easier mission
than I had expected it to be.

988
01:06:21,680 --> 01:06:24,700
- Yeah, it was a pretty simple mission.
- We could've succeeded it.

989
01:06:24,710 --> 01:06:28,220
We could've succeeded it if we had
just a little bit more time.

990
01:06:28,220 --> 01:06:29,690
We could've done it if Suk Jin
hadn't ripped the bag open.

991
01:06:29,690 --> 01:06:33,110
But is the secret couple trying to get in
the way of us succeeding the missions?

992
01:06:33,110 --> 01:06:35,670
- Why would they do that?
- To prevent us from getting the hint.

993
01:06:35,670 --> 01:06:38,050
- You think?
- How is it you know all that so well?

994
01:06:38,050 --> 01:06:41,040
- That means you're the girl!
- I was the first one to get back here.

995
01:06:41,040 --> 01:06:43,880
- Your face looks like you're lying.
- Each partner...

996
01:06:45,350 --> 01:06:48,210
[These two are acting like
they're suspicious of others.]

997
01:06:48,210 --> 01:06:50,410
- Really?
- One girl and one guy.

998
01:06:50,410 --> 01:06:52,180
The culprits are in this room.

999
01:06:52,180 --> 01:06:55,680
[Then where else would they be?]

1000
01:06:59,550 --> 01:07:01,920
- Do we go with the same partner?
- Let's just keep the same partner.

1001
01:07:01,920 --> 01:07:03,470
I like my partner.

1002
01:07:03,470 --> 01:07:06,810
But if we keep the same partner,
it'll be hard for us to figure out who it is.

1003
01:07:06,810 --> 01:07:10,050
- If we keep the same partner...
- Then let's change partners.

1004
01:07:10,050 --> 01:07:11,640
Okay, fine.

1005
01:07:12,070 --> 01:07:16,690
[Is Blank Ji trying to avoid suspicion,
or is she...]

1006
01:07:18,220 --> 01:07:21,820
- The girls will choose the partner this time.
- Okay.

1007
01:07:21,820 --> 01:07:23,270
[The girl's turn to choose the partner.]

1008
01:07:24,350 --> 01:07:26,460
[Miss Capable, Jong Sook,
to choose the first partner.]

1009
01:07:31,110 --> 01:07:32,520
Let's go together.

1010
01:07:34,030 --> 01:07:35,560
Are you kidding me?
Get lost.

1011
01:07:36,500 --> 01:07:38,960
[Immediately cuts him off.]

1012
01:07:46,180 --> 01:07:49,010
[Physically strong girl student
is turned down from her selection.]

1013
01:07:49,700 --> 01:07:51,410
What do you think you're doing?

1014
01:07:52,480 --> 01:07:54,310
[You just wait and see...]

1015
01:07:57,650 --> 01:07:59,210
You'd better make the right choice.

1016
01:07:59,940 --> 01:08:02,230
[Jong Suk breaking out into a dance
to get her to choose him?]

1017
01:08:06,550 --> 01:08:08,420
Come out.

1018
01:08:08,420 --> 01:08:10,550
[Chooses Jong Suk as expected.]

1019
01:08:11,830 --> 01:08:13,870
She meant you.

1020
01:08:13,870 --> 01:08:16,110
Lee Jong Suk's mine!

1021
01:08:16,110 --> 01:08:17,140
Sorry to ask this,
but can you all leave Jae Suk?

1022
01:08:17,140 --> 01:08:19,480
Okay, we won't choose him.

1023
01:08:19,480 --> 01:08:22,510
- Come on, Bo Young.
- Choose me.

1024
01:08:22,510 --> 01:08:26,290
- You hurt my feelings earlier.
- You and I are a perfect match.

1025
01:08:26,300 --> 01:08:27,660
[Haroro is offering
his similar height to her?]

1026
01:08:30,980 --> 01:08:33,180
- We worked really well together earlier.
- Don't think of doing anything foolish.

1027
01:08:33,960 --> 01:08:35,230
Let's go!

1028
01:08:36,840 --> 01:08:39,870
[Ji Hyo's their last hope.]

1029
01:08:39,870 --> 01:08:41,690
He's my living hell, Ji Hyo.

1030
01:08:42,680 --> 01:08:45,680
[The two grim reapers.]

1031
01:08:45,680 --> 01:08:47,950
- Ji Hyo.
- Come on, Ji Hyo.

1032
01:08:47,950 --> 01:08:49,610
- Here, Ji Hyo.
- Are you mad?

1033
01:08:50,700 --> 01:08:52,750
- Are you mad?
- What are you doing?

1034
01:08:52,750 --> 01:08:54,770
[Chooses her Monday boyfriend, Gary.]

1035
01:08:54,800 --> 01:08:59,100
- Why would I be mad?
- Don't you even have any self-respect?

1036
01:09:00,140 --> 01:09:03,030
[The Monday couple is back together again.]

1037
01:09:03,030 --> 01:09:04,720
It's our turn now, right?

1038
01:09:08,210 --> 01:09:11,950
- They're our ghosts.
- The two worst nightmares.

1039
01:09:13,520 --> 01:09:16,110
Hey, give me my chance to get revenge.

1040
01:09:17,320 --> 01:09:19,200
Aren't we free to choose
whom we love?

1041
01:09:20,870 --> 01:09:23,490
Even though we're both girls,
and friends...

1042
01:09:23,490 --> 01:09:27,120
- One, two, three.
- You.

1043
01:09:29,480 --> 01:09:31,540
[Jae Suk chooses Kwang Ja without
even a moment's hesitation.]

1044
01:09:32,330 --> 01:09:34,880
[Jong Sook is refused for the second time.]

1045
01:09:35,130 --> 01:09:37,230
He's about to explode.

1046
01:09:40,190 --> 01:09:42,550
[Totally at a loss for words.]

1047
01:09:43,380 --> 01:09:45,770
[The two must stick together
no matter what happens now.]

1048
01:09:45,770 --> 01:09:48,890
Those two are really suspicious.
Don't you think?

1049
01:09:48,890 --> 01:09:50,020
Yes, I agree.

1050
01:09:50,020 --> 01:09:54,640
[Jae Suk and Kwang Ja are suddenly
receiving everyone's suspicions.]

1051
01:09:54,640 --> 01:09:57,600
The way I see it,
those two are the real couple.

1052
01:09:57,610 --> 01:09:59,570
I bet it's those two.

1053
01:09:59,570 --> 01:10:01,250
Just wait until I get my hands
on you two.

1054
01:10:04,220 --> 01:10:07,400
[Okay... things are going well.]

1055
01:10:08,720 --> 01:10:10,580
- You have to be back within three minutes.
- Okay.

1056
01:10:10,580 --> 01:10:12,570
[Off to complete their shopping
within three minutes.]

1057
01:10:12,570 --> 01:10:14,160
We just buy whatever we want again?

1058
01:10:15,990 --> 01:10:19,520
[Out with your partner with
your hands held tight!]

1059
01:10:23,190 --> 01:10:25,440
Are you a part of a secret couple?

1060
01:10:25,440 --> 01:10:28,300
[Sae Young bluntly asks
Jong Suk the question.]

1061
01:10:29,180 --> 01:10:31,020
What do you mean, a couple?

1062
01:10:34,310 --> 01:10:35,570
No, I'm not.

1063
01:10:37,550 --> 01:10:41,080
[They're all starting to seriously
suspect one another.]

1064
01:10:41,080 --> 01:10:43,420
- I think the real couple is together now.
- I think so too.

1065
01:10:43,420 --> 01:10:46,240
- I feel suspicious of Kwang Soo.
- Me too.

1066
01:10:46,240 --> 01:10:51,450
I think the real couple is together right now
and planning something.

1067
01:10:51,450 --> 01:10:53,010
[Big-nose's sharp deductions.]

1068
01:10:53,010 --> 01:10:57,190
- We want to buy a pair of shoes.
- We'd like a buy a pair of shoes.

1069
01:10:57,190 --> 01:10:58,750
[Jae Suk and Kwang Ja wants to buy
a pair of shoes.]

1070
01:10:59,720 --> 01:11:01,530
How about a pair of slippers?

1071
01:11:01,530 --> 01:11:03,860
12,000 won?
The furry ones are pretty.

1072
01:11:04,450 --> 01:11:07,060
Here's 12,000 won.
Thank you! Good luck!

1073
01:11:07,060 --> 01:11:09,630
Okay, let's get going.

1074
01:11:09,970 --> 01:11:14,200
[Suk Jin and Jong Sook are busy tailing
their suspects, Jae Suk and Kwang Ja.]

1075
01:11:15,120 --> 01:11:16,500
What are you two planning?

1076
01:11:16,500 --> 01:11:18,460
- It's not you, is it, Bo Young?
- No, it's not.

1077
01:11:18,460 --> 01:11:21,620
- I think it may be Sae Young.
- But I'm suspicious of you too.

1078
01:11:21,620 --> 01:11:23,860
It really isn't me.

1079
01:11:24,340 --> 01:11:27,190
- I think it's Sae Young.
- I think it's you.

1080
01:11:27,190 --> 01:11:28,850
[Everyone's starting to suspect one another.]

1081
01:11:29,880 --> 01:11:32,390
[All the pairs are starting to make their
way back with their purchased items.]

1082
01:11:33,850 --> 01:11:36,380
[Ji Hyo and Gary brings back
a bag of red beans.]

1083
01:11:36,900 --> 01:11:41,400
[Stand still with all the items purchased held
between you and your partner's body.]

1084
01:11:41,400 --> 01:11:43,460
You're not talking about just
one bean, right?

1085
01:11:43,460 --> 01:11:44,640
Yes, just one bean.

1086
01:11:47,030 --> 01:11:49,120
Look at how happy Gary is.

1087
01:11:49,130 --> 01:11:51,480
Just one bean?

1088
01:11:51,480 --> 01:11:54,600
[Keep the item held by your cheeks with your
partner for one full minute.]

1089
01:11:54,600 --> 01:11:56,780
[Even the shoes?]

1090
01:11:57,890 --> 01:11:59,860
- Together?
- Yes, but we haven't started it yet.

1091
01:11:59,860 --> 01:12:02,450
Was this game created specifically
for Gary and Ji Hyo?

1092
01:12:02,450 --> 01:12:05,120
- You'd better not drop it.
- There's no way that we can drop this.

1093
01:12:05,120 --> 01:12:06,920
[Still remaining suspicious of one another
even as they stand there cheek to cheek.]

1094
01:12:09,040 --> 01:12:11,740
[Totally stuck together.]

1095
01:12:12,860 --> 01:12:14,670
[Start]

1096
01:12:15,660 --> 01:12:18,910
- Be careful.
- You're the one acting suspicious.

1097
01:12:19,930 --> 01:12:22,270
- You're acting really strange.
- I feel like it's slipping.

1098
01:12:26,370 --> 01:12:29,100
- You can't drop it.
- Dropping it would be suspicious.

1099
01:12:29,100 --> 01:12:33,050
[Will become subjects of a lot of suspicion
if they were to fail this mission.]

1100
01:12:33,060 --> 01:12:35,830
You'd be more than just suspected.

1101
01:12:36,450 --> 01:12:38,520
Let's go for five minutes of this.

1102
01:12:39,910 --> 01:12:41,360
Come on, Jong Suk.

1103
01:12:41,780 --> 01:12:43,950
[Everyone's doing a good job
of maintaining their stance...]

1104
01:12:44,660 --> 01:12:48,870
[15 seconds left to go.]

1105
01:12:52,680 --> 01:12:54,600
- Seven...
- I bet the couple is sweating bullets.

1106
01:12:55,960 --> 01:12:59,370
[Only five seconds left to go!]

1107
01:13:03,640 --> 01:13:05,750
[Pass]

1108
01:13:08,920 --> 01:13:10,780
He won't go away!

1109
01:13:13,650 --> 01:13:15,820
Are we going to keep going
with the same partner?

1110
01:13:15,820 --> 01:13:18,030
My partner and I are going to stay together.

1111
01:13:18,030 --> 01:13:20,930
- Shall we swap partners?
- I guess you're all done with scheming?

1112
01:13:20,940 --> 01:13:23,730
What are you talking about?
What scheming are you talking about?

1113
01:13:23,730 --> 01:13:25,660
[Did he catch on to the fact that there
are secret couple missions?]

1114
01:13:25,950 --> 01:13:27,220
It's not me.

1115
01:13:27,220 --> 01:13:29,030
- You two are caught.
- It's not me.

1116
01:13:31,110 --> 01:13:32,550
- Is Ji Suk Jin going to start again?
- Yes.

1117
01:13:34,400 --> 01:13:36,000
You can't hit anyone, Jong Sook.

1118
01:13:36,000 --> 01:13:40,120
- You can't hit anyone on a TV show.
- They're fighting over Yoo Jae Suk right now.

1119
01:13:41,730 --> 01:13:43,270
I'm seriously going to lose my mind.

1120
01:13:44,310 --> 01:13:47,470
[Fighting over their love for Jae Suk?]

1121
01:13:47,950 --> 01:13:51,520
And Jong Sook keeps threatening us
not to touch Jae Suk.

1122
01:13:51,520 --> 01:13:54,780
- I'm really going to lose my mind.
- I'm going to drive you crazy.

1123
01:13:56,520 --> 01:13:57,710
Shall I get started?

1124
01:13:58,960 --> 01:14:03,290
[Suk Jin, Bo Young and Gary, Ji Hyo
are already partnered up together...]

1125
01:14:03,290 --> 01:14:05,930
[Jong Suk and Sae Young are
partnered up together again.]

1126
01:14:05,930 --> 01:14:08,000
- I'm going to lose it.
- I'm going to lose it again.

1127
01:14:08,640 --> 01:14:10,760
Can you get out of the way, Jong Suk?

1128
01:14:10,770 --> 01:14:14,790
[Frightening moment in time...]

1129
01:14:16,410 --> 01:14:19,180
- It's our time.
- You'd better listen to me this time.

1130
01:14:20,420 --> 01:14:22,060
Ha Ha is to make his choice, right?

1131
01:14:23,340 --> 01:14:25,810
It's my turn to pick?
That's simple.

1132
01:14:30,650 --> 01:14:31,900
Okay, fine.

1133
01:14:33,110 --> 01:14:34,380
Come here.

1134
01:14:36,970 --> 01:14:38,480
Come here, and carry the bag.

1135
01:14:39,290 --> 01:14:40,900
I said, pick up the bag.

1136
01:14:40,910 --> 01:14:42,680
Pick up and carry the bag.

1137
01:14:47,130 --> 01:14:49,270
- Hold my hand.
- I'm going to lose it.

1138
01:14:49,270 --> 01:14:51,750
- Should I give you five minutes?
- I'm going to lose my mind.

1139
01:14:51,750 --> 01:14:54,110
- Why are you giving us five minutes?
- Give us five minutes.

1140
01:14:56,390 --> 01:14:58,100
- Lead the way.
- Lets go.

1141
01:15:03,600 --> 01:15:05,990
I don't know what to buy.

1142
01:15:06,320 --> 01:15:10,600
- How about leggings like these?
- Yeah, that looks good.

1143
01:15:11,470 --> 01:15:14,690
[Jae Suk is trying to end their shopping trip
as quickly as he can.]

1144
01:15:15,230 --> 01:15:17,580
- We're getting some leggings.
- Some new leggings for Jong Sook.

1145
01:15:18,640 --> 01:15:20,970
- We'll take these leggings.
- How much is this?

1146
01:15:20,980 --> 01:15:23,490
Here are a pair of black ones.
Let's go with the black ones.

1147
01:15:24,140 --> 01:15:25,980
Just buy whatever.

1148
01:15:25,980 --> 01:15:28,500
I'm going to go with the black one.
I didn't know there was a black one.

1149
01:15:29,140 --> 01:15:31,180
Hold my hand.

1150
01:15:31,180 --> 01:15:33,570
This is just like living hell.

1151
01:15:35,220 --> 01:15:37,830
Don't walk too fast,
and don't walk too slow either.

1152
01:15:39,080 --> 01:15:43,110
- Not too fast... and not too slow either.
- Listen, Jong Sook.

1153
01:15:43,110 --> 01:15:44,890
I'm walking alongside you right now.

1154
01:15:44,900 --> 01:15:46,910
[Jae Suk is exhausted from having to
cater to Jong Sook's needs.]

1155
01:15:46,910 --> 01:15:49,080
You two must be the couple.

1156
01:15:49,080 --> 01:15:50,910
- You two look good together.
- Don't we look good together?

1157
01:15:50,910 --> 01:15:53,540
- How long have you been together?
- It hasn't been that long.

1158
01:15:53,540 --> 01:15:55,730
We haven't been dating long,
but we're going to break up soon.

1159
01:15:55,730 --> 01:15:58,270
How can you say such a thing?
I'm not going in there.

1160
01:15:58,270 --> 01:16:00,400
Okay, I'm sorry!

1161
01:16:00,400 --> 01:16:03,170
[Jong Sook is mad by Jae Suk's comment.]

1162
01:16:03,170 --> 01:16:05,120
- Are you breaking up with me?
- No!

1163
01:16:08,280 --> 01:16:11,210
- Don't be in such a hurry.
- Okay, Honey.

1164
01:16:15,150 --> 01:16:17,380
You won't believe what we bought.

1165
01:16:19,830 --> 01:16:22,190
[Something unbelievable?]

1166
01:16:22,190 --> 01:16:24,120
[A bowl of rice?]

1167
01:16:24,120 --> 01:16:27,400
- What if this is an eating mission?
- I've got her.

1168
01:16:28,420 --> 01:16:32,170
- How can you treat a girl like that?
- If you can't eat, then you're the bad guy.

1169
01:16:35,460 --> 01:16:38,620
[All the couples make their way back
with their purchased items.]

1170
01:16:41,250 --> 01:16:42,460
You pick it.

1171
01:16:42,460 --> 01:16:43,790
I love you.

1172
01:16:45,360 --> 01:16:47,510
<i>[Word relay with the item you bought.]

1173
01:16:47,510 --> 01:16:51,250
[Word relay game within 30 seconds.]

1174
01:16:53,980 --> 01:16:57,160
- Delicious kodari.
- Delicious kodari.

1175
01:16:57,160 --> 01:17:00,550
P... Pretty leggings that you can buy
from a R-el cart.

1176
01:17:00,550 --> 01:17:04,360
S... delicious seaweed that even
the stars enjoy eating.

1177
01:17:05,950 --> 01:17:09,450
K... A filling kkot-gam that
I can eat when I feel empty and hungry.

1178
01:17:09,450 --> 01:17:12,430
Gam... Gamsa (thanks) for the delicious
bowl of rice!

1179
01:17:12,430 --> 01:17:14,470
- We did it.
- Yeah, we did it.

1180
01:17:17,550 --> 01:17:20,660
[Mission success]

1181
01:17:20,660 --> 01:17:22,220
We did it.

1182
01:17:22,220 --> 01:17:25,250
Both teams will receive their own hints.

1183
01:17:25,250 --> 01:17:26,840
[Both teams to receive a set of hints from
having succeeded two rounds of the mission.]

1184
01:17:26,850 --> 01:17:31,450
[Succeed the secret couple mission, then it's
real and fake hint. If not, just a real hint.]

1185
01:17:31,450 --> 01:17:33,140
Are they both real hints?

1186
01:17:33,140 --> 01:17:35,940
- It's one real, and one fake hint.
- Which ones are for which team?

1187
01:17:35,940 --> 01:17:37,600
[A real and a fake hint?]

1188
01:17:37,600 --> 01:17:40,550
[Wait... there being two hints means...]

1189
01:17:41,300 --> 01:17:44,800
[During their first shopping trip...]

1190
01:17:44,810 --> 01:17:47,800
[While no one was
paying them any attention...]

1191
01:17:54,880 --> 01:17:59,080
[Even with Jae Suk, Bo Young, Suk Jin
and Sae Young right next to them...]

1192
01:18:00,450 --> 01:18:06,170
[They boldly succeeded their
secret couple mission!]

1193
01:18:16,750 --> 01:18:19,240
- We did it, right?
- Yes, I think we did.

1194
01:18:24,690 --> 01:18:27,770
[Even after being the first ones
to arrive back...]

1195
01:18:27,770 --> 01:18:31,200
[They do the mission again just in case
the first attempt wasn't valid.]

1196
01:18:33,570 --> 01:18:36,290
[The secret mission is definitely a success!]

1197
01:18:36,290 --> 01:18:39,040
This was my third time.
What have I done to deserve this?

1198
01:18:40,410 --> 01:18:41,690
They're coming.

1199
01:18:41,690 --> 01:18:44,570
[That's how the secret mission was completed.]

1200
01:18:44,570 --> 01:18:47,380
[Thus, one real and one fake hint.]

1201
01:18:47,380 --> 01:18:48,830
- Bye.
- I love you.

1202
01:18:48,830 --> 01:18:51,230
- Bye Jong Sook.
- Bye.

1203
01:18:51,230 --> 01:18:53,660
- It was fun.
- Yeah, right.

1204
01:18:54,450 --> 01:18:56,280
Don't think that we're over for good.

1205
01:18:58,100 --> 01:18:59,520
What does this mean?

1206
01:18:59,520 --> 01:19:00,890
What is this?

1207
01:19:01,720 --> 01:19:03,200
- What is this?
- What does that mean?

1208
01:19:03,200 --> 01:19:06,990
Don't you think that this is a phone number
or a text message of some sorts?

1209
01:19:07,000 --> 01:19:08,760
[Could it be related to a phone number?]

1210
01:19:08,760 --> 01:19:11,000
- It's possible.
- What phone number?

1211
01:19:14,550 --> 01:19:18,820
[Difficult to make a correct guess since
the fake hint is mixed in there.]

1212
01:19:18,820 --> 01:19:20,230
I got it.

1213
01:19:20,230 --> 01:19:21,830
Okay, let's go.

1214
01:19:21,830 --> 01:19:24,040
It means that one of them is real.

1215
01:19:28,310 --> 01:19:33,060
[Real hint and a fake hint.]

1216
01:19:33,060 --> 01:19:36,710
- Wait, we need to figure out the hint.
- I know what it means.

1217
01:19:38,170 --> 01:19:41,930
[The mysterious number stands for
a person's name?]

1218
01:19:41,930 --> 01:19:44,480
Then we need to figure out
who's name it is?

1219
01:19:44,480 --> 01:19:47,420
[If they start decoding the numbers...]

1220
01:19:47,420 --> 01:19:50,040
[It means it's either
Park Bo Young and Gary...]

1221
01:19:50,040 --> 01:19:52,890
[Or Song Ji Hyo and Lee Jong Suk.]

1222
01:19:52,890 --> 01:19:54,960
- Why?
- Yeah, it's definitely Park Bo Young.

1223
01:19:54,960 --> 01:19:58,020
No, think about the very first
set of clues that we got.

1224
01:19:58,650 --> 01:20:01,160
Then what does that mean?
Who's the real culprit?

1225
01:20:01,160 --> 01:20:02,240
- Hey, Jong Suk.
- Yes?

1226
01:20:02,250 --> 01:20:04,600
- Be honest with us.
- It really isn't me.

1227
01:20:04,600 --> 01:20:07,190
- It's not you?
- I haven't even done anything all day!

1228
01:20:08,260 --> 01:20:10,240
- Jong Suk, is it you?
- No, it's not me.

1229
01:20:10,660 --> 01:20:13,550
Me and Bo Young?
What year was Bo Young born in?

1230
01:20:13,950 --> 01:20:16,510
- Bo Young was born in '94.
- She's 24 years old.

1231
01:20:16,510 --> 01:20:20,620
[The second set of numbers is '12'.
Could it be Bo Young and Gary's age gap?]

1232
01:20:21,550 --> 01:20:23,200
It's Kang Gary.

1233
01:20:23,200 --> 01:20:27,200
[Gary and Bo Young are the likely suspects
from what the numbers are indicating?]

1234
01:20:27,800 --> 01:20:32,010
[Please... don't change
your minds about that!]

1235
01:20:33,050 --> 01:20:37,260
[The final location-
School field in Haejeomun.]

1236
01:20:37,260 --> 01:20:40,540
[A giant sized picture frame and
a camera covered in flour?]

1237
01:20:40,550 --> 01:20:44,420
[Is it Jong Suk and Ji Hyo...
or Gary and Bo Young?]

1238
01:20:44,420 --> 01:20:46,030
- Wouldn't I be too obvious?
- That's why it's you.

1239
01:20:46,030 --> 01:20:47,670
There they come.

1240
01:20:49,280 --> 01:20:50,650
What?

1241
01:20:50,650 --> 01:20:53,250
- Maybe it's not her.
- Bo Young is next.

1242
01:20:54,310 --> 01:20:57,510
But keep this in mind.
We have an extra hint that you don't.

1243
01:20:57,510 --> 01:21:01,540
[They have an extra hint
that the other team doesn't?]

1244
01:21:01,540 --> 01:21:04,320
[A hint that we don't have?]

1245
01:21:04,470 --> 01:21:07,960
[All the members walking to pottery village
before they did the market mission.]

1246
01:21:08,780 --> 01:21:11,480
[These two are assuming some sort of
a position even here?]

1247
01:21:11,480 --> 01:21:13,810
I'm going to lose my mind.
You all keep thinking it's me?

1248
01:21:14,180 --> 01:21:18,270
[No way... you want me to do that?]

1249
01:21:18,810 --> 01:21:21,940
[The ultimate gesture- The back hug.]

1250
01:21:23,440 --> 01:21:25,140
[That's too hard.]

1251
01:21:27,850 --> 01:21:30,880
[The mission that they did here is
'The game of love'.]

1252
01:21:30,880 --> 01:21:35,100
Yoo Jae Suk will make a heart sign with his
hands and point it towards someone.

1253
01:21:35,100 --> 01:21:36,620
He'll direct his heart to the next person.

1254
01:21:36,620 --> 01:21:41,010
If Song Ji Hyo accepts,
then she'll do the same thing to Ha Ha.

1255
01:21:41,010 --> 01:21:42,880
So it'll go around
in a circle in that manner.

1256
01:21:42,880 --> 01:21:45,740
If you don't want to accept
Yoo Jae Suk's love...

1257
01:21:45,740 --> 01:21:48,610
then you can choose your own method
to refuse his love.

1258
01:21:48,620 --> 01:21:50,360
[Can refuse his love in any methods
that you choose should you decide to refuse.]

1259
01:21:52,450 --> 01:21:55,200
[Will we be able to...]

1260
01:21:55,200 --> 01:22:00,280
[do a back hug here?]

1261
01:22:00,280 --> 01:22:04,760
Will the person accept it or not!
The game of love!

1262
01:22:06,950 --> 01:22:08,360
I love you.

1263
01:22:09,970 --> 01:22:11,400
I love you.

1264
01:22:15,400 --> 01:22:17,520
- I love you.
- Love you too.

1265
01:22:23,420 --> 01:22:27,230
[Mr. Gary's sincerity leaking through?]

1266
01:22:27,230 --> 01:22:30,100
- Gary needs to get punished.
- Must I get punished for that?

1267
01:22:30,110 --> 01:22:31,690
[Punishment is a kiss on the cheek,
befitting of the love game.]

1268
01:22:34,110 --> 01:22:38,050
[Sae Young and Bo Young's
double cheek kiss.]

1269
01:22:38,050 --> 01:22:40,340
Hurray!
Mother!

1270
01:22:42,340 --> 01:22:48,960
[It's not the kiss we need,
but a back hug we need...]

1271
01:22:49,500 --> 01:22:51,690
I just hope that Kwang Soo
doesn't come sit next to me.

1272
01:22:51,690 --> 01:22:52,960
[Time to swap seats.]

1273
01:22:53,480 --> 01:22:56,890
[Okay... Blank Ji is now sitting
now to Jong Suk.]

1274
01:22:56,890 --> 01:23:00,280
[She is sitting next to me now...]

1275
01:23:00,290 --> 01:23:03,120
[But suddenly feeling shy about doing it.]

1276
01:23:04,120 --> 01:23:05,720
I love you.

1277
01:23:06,000 --> 01:23:07,670
I love you.

1278
01:23:08,880 --> 01:23:10,640
[Back hug]

1279
01:23:15,500 --> 01:23:17,540
[I don't think now's the time.]

1280
01:23:23,490 --> 01:23:26,190
[Automatically breaks out in a fit
of laughter upon seeing Kwang Ja's face.]

1281
01:23:26,850 --> 01:23:30,690
[I'm too embarrassed to do
the back hug!]

1282
01:23:30,690 --> 01:23:33,300
Here's your real hint.

1283
01:23:33,300 --> 01:23:35,280
[Only the real hint is given out
from having failed the secret mission.]

1284
01:23:36,140 --> 01:23:39,930
[We're in trouble...]

1285
01:23:40,790 --> 01:23:44,190
[Thus, the girl team earned themselves
an extra real hint.]

1286
01:23:44,550 --> 01:23:46,050
'Let's start a business'?

1287
01:23:46,050 --> 01:23:49,390
[What does this hint mean?]

1288
01:23:50,020 --> 01:23:52,930
- Are you guys still figuring it out?
- Let's move it along.

1289
01:23:52,930 --> 01:23:54,730
[The hint is making a difference
in what the two teams know?]

1290
01:23:54,740 --> 01:24:01,340
[They're still confused over whether it's
Jong Suk, Ji Hyo or Gary, Bo Young.]

1291
01:24:01,340 --> 01:24:04,960
He keeps denying that it's him,
but why aren't you doing the same?

1292
01:24:04,960 --> 01:24:07,400
- I told you earlier that it isn't me.
- Who do you think it is?

1293
01:24:07,400 --> 01:24:09,090
I think it's Jae Suk.

1294
01:24:09,450 --> 01:24:14,160
[Jong Suk is flustered from being cornered,
and still pointing fingers at Jae Suk.]

1295
01:24:16,560 --> 01:24:18,550
What is taking you guys so long?

1296
01:24:18,550 --> 01:24:20,830
- No other choice.
- Okay, we got it.

1297
01:24:20,830 --> 01:24:23,000
- We got it.
- We've made our decision.

1298
01:24:25,440 --> 01:24:28,870
[Secret couple, Ji Hyo and Jong Suk.
Can they still keep their secret?]

1299
01:24:29,380 --> 01:24:35,590
The male team will announce who they think is
the secret couple from having arrived first

1300
01:24:35,600 --> 01:24:38,210
and ask the couple to stand in front
of the frame that you seeing the middle.

1301
01:24:38,210 --> 01:24:40,750
[Please...]

1302
01:24:40,750 --> 01:24:43,620
- Okay, I'm going to count to five.
- Ji Hyo and Jong Suk.

1303
01:24:43,630 --> 01:24:45,660
- Okay, let's go with Ji Hyo and Jong Suk.
- Why?

1304
01:24:45,660 --> 01:24:47,210
- It's Ji Hyo and Jong Suk.
- Why?

1305
01:24:47,210 --> 01:24:50,380
- Look at how confident Ji Hyo looks.
- But she's an actress.

1306
01:24:50,380 --> 01:24:52,460
[Blank Ji is maintaining her poker face
all the way to the end.]

1307
01:24:52,460 --> 01:24:55,770
[Last minute chance to Gary?]

1308
01:24:56,140 --> 01:24:58,280
No, you've gotten much better
at lying lately.

1309
01:24:58,280 --> 01:25:01,358
What are you talking about?
Think about our Christmas special.

1310
01:25:01,358 --> 01:25:05,410
[Nervous... and anxious.]

1311
01:25:05,410 --> 01:25:08,040
What are you talking about?
Think about our Christmas special.

1312
01:25:08,040 --> 01:25:09,830
No, we can't even tell when you're
lying to us anymore.

1313
01:25:09,830 --> 01:25:13,020
Then I'll go stand up there right now.

1314
01:25:13,020 --> 01:25:15,270
Just hang on a second.

1315
01:25:15,580 --> 01:25:17,910
[The team is going back and forth
on their decision to the very last minute.]

1316
01:25:17,910 --> 01:25:19,950
[Please...]

1317
01:25:22,060 --> 01:25:23,760
Song Ji Hyo and Lee Jong Suk.

1318
01:25:24,260 --> 01:25:30,680
[Normally standoffish Ji Hyo was being
unusually friendly with Jong Suk today?]

1319
01:25:31,350 --> 01:25:35,030
Lee Jong Suk and Song Ji Hyo.

1320
01:25:35,540 --> 01:25:40,830
[Ah... our secret love affair...
Will this be the end of it?]

1321
01:25:42,590 --> 01:25:48,750
[Jong Suk and Ji Hyo are ultimately made
to go stand in front of the picture frame.]

1322
01:25:50,440 --> 01:25:54,060
[Preparing themselves to get showered
with the flour.]

1323
01:25:55,060 --> 01:25:56,660
Okay, time to take the picture.

1324
01:25:56,660 --> 01:25:59,990
[You did great today.]

1325
01:26:00,550 --> 01:26:05,390
One, two...

1326
01:26:06,600 --> 01:26:08,060
Two...

1327
01:26:08,570 --> 01:26:11,840
[The camera of truth!]

1328
01:26:23,000 --> 01:26:26,180
- I knew that it was you two.
- I wasn't absolutely sure though.

1329
01:26:26,180 --> 01:26:29,280
- What made you so sure?
- The numbers.

1330
01:26:29,280 --> 01:26:32,610
And Jong Suk kept acting nervous.

1331
01:26:32,610 --> 01:26:36,600
It was either Gary or Jong Suk...
and Gary kept working on solving the hint.

1332
01:26:36,600 --> 01:26:39,100
- But Jong Suk didn't do that.
- He didn't want to solve the hint.

1333
01:26:39,110 --> 01:26:40,380
[Too bad.]

1334
01:26:40,380 --> 01:26:43,100
- The extra hint that we got is amazing.
- What is it?

1335
01:26:43,100 --> 01:26:45,250
'Let's start a business'.

1336
01:26:45,250 --> 01:26:46,850
What does that mean?

1337
01:26:46,860 --> 01:26:51,050
Look at the letters of it all.
It spells out Song Ji Hyo and Lee Jong Suk.

1338
01:26:52,720 --> 01:26:56,720
I knew something was off.
I felt kind of crappy all day long.

1339
01:26:56,720 --> 01:26:58,450
- They were too close all day.
- Did they not have any missions?

1340
01:26:58,450 --> 01:27:00,760
- We had a lot of missions to do.
- You did?

1341
01:27:00,760 --> 01:27:03,590
What did you guys do?

1342
01:27:03,590 --> 01:27:06,800
The first mission was to
clasp our hands together.

1343
01:27:07,530 --> 01:27:09,290
I saw the producers holding their hands!

1344
01:27:09,290 --> 01:27:11,190
- Who did?
- Why you...

1345
01:27:12,650 --> 01:27:14,820
I misunderstood and
thought that they were dating.

1346
01:27:14,820 --> 01:27:18,040
[They were just working hard
at their jobs.]

1347
01:27:18,040 --> 01:27:20,370
I thought that Jong Suk really liked
Ji Hyo for real.

1348
01:27:20,850 --> 01:27:23,040
But I should've known better.
That's not possible.

1349
01:27:23,040 --> 01:27:25,590
I guess Gary can go back to
enjoying eating again.

1350
01:27:25,590 --> 01:27:27,950
What about Jong Suk?

1351
01:27:27,950 --> 01:27:30,730
I told you that I'm not good at things
like this, and not to make me do it.

1352
01:27:30,730 --> 01:27:33,890
- I'm not good at things like this.
- It's because Jong Suk is too pure.

1353
01:27:34,214 --> 01:27:35,214
Subtitles by DramaFever

1354
01:27:35,214 --> 01:27:37,850
<i>[Viewer's choice guest for
Running Man's 2014 episode.]

1355
01:27:37,860 --> 01:27:42,270
<i>[Yeo Jin Goo, Im Si Wan, and Do Hee.]

1356
01:27:42,270 --> 01:27:44,590
<i>Just try going for my name tag.
I'm going to come for your throat.

1357
01:27:48,320 --> 01:27:51,790
<i>[A nightmare of a mission that was sent in
by one of their fans in Hong Kong.]

1358
01:27:51,790 --> 01:27:53,940
<i>[Three set water game that
is of an unbelievable scale.]

1359
01:27:53,940 --> 01:27:57,410
<i>[The flying chair, Blob jump, and Diving.]

1360
01:27:59,700 --> 01:28:04,580
<i>[Next up is the acupuncture mat race.]

1361
01:28:04,580 --> 01:28:08,880
<i>[A race that's never been attempted before.]

1362
01:28:08,880 --> 01:28:11,460
<i>[The agony that cannot be ignored.]

1363
01:28:11,470 --> 01:28:13,430
<i>We will show you a good time
through these games!

1364
01:28:13,430 --> 01:28:15,500
<i>- I love you!
- I love Hong Kong!

1365
01:28:16,850 --> 01:28:18,480
<i>[A race from Hong Kong.]

1366
01:28:18,480 --> 01:28:21,469
<i>Running Man is so much better
when I just watch it on TV.

